reviewText: Did not know about her but support an orphanage in uganda run by a group of nuns.  It was a very nice movie.  I passed it on to a family member who does research in Uganda.  You can enjoy the movie even if you don't have any contact with the country.
Quite an eye opener of a young woman's struggle to become a great and honored doctor in Uganda. A real heart warming tear maker! Have Klenex
